ばかりか#Empt.#動＋普通形/名、名＋である/い形＋い/な形＋である#XばかりかY, X is already plenty (both bad or good) but then also Y/as if X weren't enough already, also Y/X expresses something unusual (but doesn't need to contain the thing itself see ex.) and Y adds something unexpected on top of that/Y often has a も or でも in it#友達ばかりか親兄弟も彼の居場所を知らない(X doesn't contain the unusual thing itself yet (i.e. not knowing where he is) but only the group whose not knowing this would already be plenty strange.)
